---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTABanner from '../components/sections/CTABanner.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Website Design Auckland — Fast, Professional & Affordable | SiteGenius"
  description="Professional website design in Auckland from $499. One-off fee, custom websites for Auckland businesses. SEO-optimised, mobile-first, no lock-in."
>
  <article class="pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-4xl">

      <header class="mb-16">
        <span class="text-neon-cyan font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-4 block">Website Design Auckland</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-8 leading-tight">
          Website Design <span class="gradient-text">Auckland</span> — Built to Win Customers
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-muted-200 max-w-3xl">
          Auckland businesses need more than a nice-looking website — they need one that shows up on Google, loads fast, and turns visitors into leads. That's exactly what SiteGenius builds.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/get-a-quote" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
          <a href="/portfolio" class="btn-secondary">See Our Work</a>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none">

        <div class="glass p-8 mb-12 rounded-3xl border border-neon-cyan/20">
          <p class="text-lg font-medium text-muted-100 leading-relaxed m-0">
            Auckland is one of the most competitive markets in New Zealand. If your website isn't fast, professional, and visible on Google — you're invisible to the customers searching for you right now. SiteGenius helps Auckland businesses fix that.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Why Your Auckland Business Needs a Proper Website</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-200 mb-6">
          Over 90% of consumers research a business online before making contact. In Auckland, that number is even higher — this is one of the most digitally active cities in New Zealand. A weak website doesn't just fail to impress — it actively costs you customers.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted-200 mb-6">
          A properly built website in Auckland needs to:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 text-muted-200">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-neon-cyan font-bold mt-1">→</span><span><strong class="text-muted-100">Load in under 2 seconds</strong> — Auckland customers won't wait, and neither will Google.</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-neon-cyan font-bold mt-1">→</span><span><strong class="text-muted-100">Rank locally</strong> — Show up in searches like "plumber Auckland" or "accountant Newmarket".</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-neon-cyan font-bold mt-1">→</span><span><strong class="text-muted-100">Work perfectly on mobile</strong> — Over 70% of local searches happen on phones.</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-neon-cyan font-bold mt-1">→</span><span><strong class="text-muted-100">Build trust immediately</strong> — Reviews, photos, and clear information make people pick up the phone.</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-neon-cyan font-bold mt-1">→</span><span><strong class="text-muted-100">Have a clear call to action</strong> — Every page should make it easy to contact you or book.</span></li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Auckland Suburbs We Work With</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-200 mb-6">We serve businesses across the full Auckland region — from the CBD to the outer suburbs. And yes, if you're in Auckland we're happy to meet in person too.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8 not-prose">
          {[
            'Auckland CBD', 'Ponsonby', 'Grey Lynn', 'Newmarket', 'Parnell', 'Remuera', 'Epsom', 'Mt Eden', 'Kingsland', 'Avondale', 'New Lynn',
            'Henderson', 'Glen Eden', 'Waitakere', 'Massey', 'Hobsonville', 'Whenuapai', 'Kumeu', 'Helensville',
            'Takapuna', 'Devonport', 'Milford', 'Forrest Hill', 'Albany', 'North Harbour', 'Silverdale', 'Orewa', 'Whangaparaoa', 'Dairy Flat',
            'Manukau', 'Papatoetoe', 'Otahuhu', 'Mangere', 'Favona', 'Flat Bush', 'Botany', 'Howick', 'Pakuranga', 'Highland Park',
            'Papakura', 'Pukekohe', 'Waiuku', 'Beachlands', 'Clevedon', 'Hunua',
            'Mt Roskill', 'Onehunga', 'Royal Oak', 'Panmure', 'Mt Wellington', 'Glen Innes', 'Ellerslie',
          ].map(suburb => (
            <span class="glass rounded-lg px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-200">{suburb}</span>
          ))}
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Industries We Design For in Auckland</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 text-muted-200">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-neon-cyan font-bold mt-1">→</span><span><strong class="text-muted-100">Trades & Home Services</strong> — Plumbers, builders, electricians, painters, landscapers, cleaners</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-neon-cyan font-bold mt-1">→</span><span><strong class="text-muted-100">Automotive</strong> — Car dealers, mechanics, detailers, tyre shops, panel beaters</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-neon-cyan font-bold mt-1">→</span><span><strong class="text-muted-100">Real Estate & Property</strong> — Agents, property managers, developers, valuers</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-neon-cyan font-bold mt-1">→</span><span><strong class="text-muted-100">Health & Wellness</strong> — Physiotherapists, dentists, gyms, personal trainers, salons, spas</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-neon-cyan font-bold mt-1">→</span><span><strong class="text-muted-100">Hospitality & Food</strong> — Cafes, restaurants, catering, food trucks, bakeries</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-neon-cyan font-bold mt-1">→</span><span><strong class="text-muted-100">Professional Services</strong> — Accountants, lawyers, mortgage brokers, consultants, coaches</span></li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">How Much Does Website Design Cost in Auckland?</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-200 mb-6">
          The cost of website design in Auckland ranges dramatically — from $500 for a basic template build to $20,000+ at a full-service agency. Most small and medium Auckland businesses don't need to spend anywhere near that.
        </p>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8 not-prose">
          {[
            { plan: 'Starter', price: '$499', desc: '1-page site for sole traders getting online fast. One-off fee, yours forever.' },
            { plan: 'Essential', price: '$1,499', desc: '3–4 page small business site. Custom design, CMS, SEO. One-off fee.' },
            { plan: 'Professional', price: '$2,499', desc: '5–7 pages with blog, advanced SEO, and performance optimisation. One-off fee.' },
            { plan: 'Custom', price: 'Get a Quote', desc: 'E-commerce, bookings, custom features. Fixed price upfront.' },
          ].map(p => (
            <div class="glass rounded-xl p-6">
              <p class="text-neon-cyan font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">{p.plan}</p>
              <p class="text-3xl font-black text-muted-100 mb-3">{p.price}</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted-300 leading-relaxed">{p.desc}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Our Auckland Website Design Process</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8 not-prose">
          {[
            { step: '01', title: 'Free Consultation', desc: 'We learn about your Auckland business, your goals, and what your customers need to see.' },
            { step: '02', title: 'Design & Build', desc: 'We design and build your site — custom layout, your branding, your content. No templates.' },
            { step: '03', title: 'Review & Refine', desc: 'You review the site and we make adjustments until you\'re completely happy.' },
            { step: '04', title: 'Launch & Grow', desc: 'We launch your site and stay on hand for updates, support, and any future changes.' },
          ].map(item => (
            <div class="glass rounded-xl p-5 flex items-start gap-5">
              <span class="text-neon-cyan font-black text-2xl font-heading">{item.step}</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-muted-100 mb-1">{item.title}</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-muted-300">{item.desc}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-12">
          {[
            { q: 'How long does website design take in Auckland?', a: 'Most projects are completed and live within 7–14 days. For larger builds with custom functionality, 3–4 weeks is typical.' },
            { q: 'Can we meet in person?', a: 'Yes! If you\'re based in Auckland, we\'re happy to meet in person. All our work can be done 100% remotely — video calls, shared docs, and a simple review platform — but we\'re always up for a face-to-face catch-up in Auckland if that\'s your preference.' },
            { q: 'Will my Auckland website show up on Google?', a: 'Yes. Every site we build is SEO-optimised from day one, including local SEO setup targeting Auckland suburbs and your specific industry keywords.' },
            { q: 'What happens after my site goes live?', a: 'You own it outright. We offer optional hosting and care plans to keep things running smoothly — but there\'s no lock-in. We\'re here when you need us.' },
            { q: 'Can you redesign my existing Auckland website?', a: 'Absolutely. We do redesigns regularly. If your current site is slow, outdated, or not converting — we\'ll assess it and tell you exactly what needs to change.' },
          ].map(item => (
            <div class="glass rounded-xl p-6">
              <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-muted-100 mb-3">{item.q}</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-200 text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.a}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <CTABanner
    title="Ready to grow your Auckland business online?"
    description="Free quote, no obligation. We'll tell you exactly what your site needs."
    href="/get-a-quote"
    label="Get a Free Quote"
  />
</BaseLayout>
